betterquesting.name: Collect Wood
betterquesting.desc: To become the greatest modder to have ever existed, you will need some resources. Start by collecting some wood. It will be your basic material used for creating other things. Every journey has its beginning. This is yours.

betterquesting.name: Getting Started
betterquesting.desc: I see that you have done this before, so I shall give you another challenge: create one of each tool in stone and then come back.

betterquesting.name: Storage
betterquesting.desc: I see that your pockets are beginning to fill up. But fear not, as I have another task for you: create some drawers to store some of your items in.

betterquesting.name: Bigger Is Better
betterquesting.desc: I f you want extra storage, you can create this chest to store bigger amounts of items.

betterquesting.name: Let's Go Hunt!
betterquesting.desc: To maintain sanity on your quest for greatness you will need nutrition. Nutrition is obtained from eating. So this quest is fairly simple: hunt down and kill a few mobs.

betterquesting.name: Agriculture
betterquesting.desc: Plant some seeds and watch them grow over time. In the future people passing by your farm will say: "Wow, that agriculture is so mystical...."

betterquesting.name: It Actually Adds Something!
betterquesting.desc: Finally we are actually adding cool things to your arsenal. Just check the box and we can get started!

betterquesting.name: Even Bigger Is Even Better
betterquesting.desc: You must have a lot of items.

betterquesting.name: Really Big Is Really Good
betterquesting.desc: This is wayyy too big.

betterquesting.name: The Biggest Is The Bestest!
betterquesting.desc: Too. Many. Items.

betterquesting.desc: Too. Many. Items.

betterquesting.desc: If you want extra storage, you can create this chest to store bigger amounts of items.

betterquesting.desc: You must have a lot of items.

betterquesting.name: Actually All-In-One
betterquesting.desc: To become more efficient in your quest to greatness, you must think outside the box, for example, make one of these.

betterquesting.name: Botanic Garden
betterquesting.desc: Farming can be fun, but to make it even more fun, you can create these to start your very own botanical garden.

betterquesting.name: Collecting Flora
betterquesting.desc: You will notice that this mystical power requires flowers in order to be produced. Therefore, collect 1 of each.

betterquesting.name: Power To The People!
betterquesting.desc: Now, we are beginning to get industrial. But to continue on that topic, you will need power. In this pack, the mod CJCore is installed. If you are a part of CJMinecraft's community, you will know what that means. Otherwise, I can tell you that this mod can convert any energy type into any other energy type. For example, this RF generator can power an IC2 machine that uses EU. All you have to do is choose your favourite power type in the CJCore config.

betterquesting.name: Mana, mana, mana!
betterquesting.desc:
As you become more experienced with agriculture you will notice that there is a way to transfuse certain items using a mystic energy called: "mana".
The first step to obtain it is creating a mana pool, a mana spreader, and a wand of the forest.

betterquesting.name: Welcome, modder!
betterquesting.desc: Today is the day when you will arise from the peasants as the true great modder you are!

betterquesting.name: Semi-Technichal I Suppose?
betterquesting.desc: We dive into the technical aspect of your journey, creating machines and other things to extend your capabilities and simplify your tasks.
